Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:04.87,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Is this it? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの掘っ立て小屋だ…\Nただの掘っ立て小屋だぞ 漂(ひょう)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.04,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,It's just a little shack sunken into the ground. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.06,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,It's just a shack, Piao! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.54,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What the hell is this? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだよ？ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:17.40,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Without getting revenge for you... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は お前の敵討ちもせずに―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.41,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,and without knowing what was going on... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワケも分からず\Nこんな所にまで来ちまったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.16,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I came to this place! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.04,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Tell me... Piao.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えろよ 漂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.50,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What did you die for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 なんで死んじまったんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで俺をここに導いた？\Nこんなボロ小屋に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.22,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Why did you lead me... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.38,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,to this broken down shack? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.14,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What on earth is in here?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何があるっていうんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:00.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No way... That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなバカな…
