Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,P-Piao...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）古代中国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.72,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Ancient China.
