Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:15.34,Kingdom-Title-Op,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,9)}Fated Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.91,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Damn, that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人Ａ）いたたた…\Nまったく なんてガキだ ちきしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.92,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Geez, what a crazy brat! Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.53,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,I've never seen a kid that insanely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人Ｃ）あんなメチャクチャに\N強いガキ 見たことがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.61,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,He broke my damn ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:03.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あばらが折れちまったよ\N（村人Ｂ）だらしねえ野郎だな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.30,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What a bunch of sorry bastards you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:07.43,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,You still call yourselves men of Heibei Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人Ｂ）それでも\N天下に恐れられる黒卑村(こくひむら)の男か！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:11.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人Ｃ）お前に言われたくねえ\N（笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.63,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ… 違(ちげ)えねえや\Nあっ いてっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.77,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Ya got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:14.64,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？\N（村人Ｃ）おい どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.38,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.07,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Somebody... else is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また誰かが…\N（村人Ｃ）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.44,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.70,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Ey, ey. What're you doin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おうおう！\Nてめえ なに しれっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… ちょ… ちょっと待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.63,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,H-Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの姿 前に聞いたことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:56.69,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,His appearance... I've heard about it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:05:02.49,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Could... Could that be... a Zhuxiong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人Ａ）ま… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか“朱凶(しゅきょう)”？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暗殺200年の歴史を持つといわれる\N刺客の一族“朱凶”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.89,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,They're said to have a 200 year long history of assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.78,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The family of assassins, the Zhuxiongs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:13.36,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The ones who it's said that if they target you, you're as good as dead...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらに狙われたら最後\N命はないという あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He looks like him, but he's not Piao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似ているが こいつは漂じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも なぜだ？ め… 目が離せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I... can't take my eyes off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.14,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政(せい)）やはり そうか\Nお前が来たということは 漂は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.72,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,The fact that you came means that Piao...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで漂を知ってんだ？\N分からねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,How do you know Piao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は何なんだ？\Nなんで漂と同じ顔をしている？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Why do you have the same face as Piao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ俺や漂を知っている？\N一体 何なんだよ？ これは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,How do you know me and Piao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just what the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.69,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,It seems that there isn't time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明する暇はなさそうだ\N（信）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何だ？ 敵か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that? An enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（徐完(じょかん)）もはや逃がさぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.26,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,You can no longer escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命をもらうぞ　大王 嬴政(えいせい)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.01,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,Your life is mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.01,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,King Ying Zheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 大王だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,K-King...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が… この国の…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:25.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're... this state's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.78,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（徐完）ほほう… 小僧\Nお前 王の配下ではなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.98,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,Hoho. So, kid, you weren't one of the king's subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:36.27,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,The fact that you're standing here really shows your excellent use of a double...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこにいるのはな\N大層 ご立派な替え玉を使って―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく生き延びた王よ\N（信）替え玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.79,Kingdom-Main,Zhuxiong,0,0,0,,to allow you to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Double?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:43.44,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Even I'm surprised that such an identical pair of humans exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（徐完）しかし あれほど\N瓜二(うりふた)つの人間がいるとは驚きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.42,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,There'd have to be in order to fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがの俺もダマされた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも\Nなかなか すごいガキだったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:50.09,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Though that was quite an incredible brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:55.43,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,He's the first one to ever escape even after I'd dealt them a fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺が致命傷を与えながらも\N逃がしたのは ヤツが初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皮肉にも\Nそのしぶとさがアダとなって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:01.46,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Though, what a cruel twist of fate that his tenacity backfired...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺をここまで\Nたどりつかせてしまったがな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.23,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,by allowing me to reach you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:16.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Xin... Our strength and our hearts are alike...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは 力も心も等しい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,We're one in body and soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人は一心同体だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:23.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が羽ばたけば…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.97,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,If you flap your wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.67,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,I'll be... there with you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も そこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:32.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Xin... take me... with you across the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:32.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信… 俺を天下に連れていってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:40.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:41.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:41.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）漂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！ だんだん分かってきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Dammit... It's getting clearer and clearer now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が王で… お前が刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And you're the assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao was a double for the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王と瓜二つだった漂は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:11.35,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The reason he was brought to the palace in the first place was to be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から 替え玉にするために\N王宮に連れていかれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 王と間違われて殺された！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And he was mistaken for the king and killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は弟の反乱を知ってたな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You knew about your younger brother's rebellion, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:22.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So you switched places with Piao and ran away to hide in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 漂を身代わりにして\Nこんな所に逃げ隠れてやがった！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:27.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂が襲われると知っていながら\N身代わりにしたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:26.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You switched with Piao even though you knew he would be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.03,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:35.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You bastaaaard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフッ…\N面白いことになってきたな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.40,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,This has become very entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:42.98,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Kid, I think I'll allow you to kill the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小僧 なんだったら\N王を殺すのを譲ってやるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.04,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,But I'll be taking his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし 首は俺がいただくがな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 殺す　ぶっ殺してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll kill him. I'll fucking kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.67,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,That's it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ 小僧\N腕前 とくと拝見しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.38,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Let's have a thorough look at your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,A thorough look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）“とくと拝見”だと？\N（徐完）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.19,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rip out the guts of the one who killed Piao,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂を殺したお前のはらわた\N引きずり出してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.97,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,His skill with a sword is anything but ordinary. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:21.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつの剣 尋常ではない\Nしかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.33,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,But... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるな 小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.19,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Pretty good, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.14,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Your power, speed, technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力 速さ 技… どれも\N漂とかという替え玉と ほぼ同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.83,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,They're all nearly a perfect match of that of the double you called Piao or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:33.96,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,But still, it's just a superficial sword that has never tasted blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 所詮\N血を吸ったことのない小手先の剣だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で… でかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.39,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,H-He's huge! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺に戦いを挑もうなど\N100年 早いわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:46.80,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,You're a hundred years too early to even try to challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.09,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.36,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,You've done nothing but waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダに時間をつぶした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嬴政… 覚悟を決めろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.89,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Ying Zheng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.59,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:36.15,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(820,820)\pos(666,513)}State of Qin   Xianyang
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（迫氏(さこし)）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:07.81,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,513)}King's Younger Brother, Chenjiao
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（成蟜(せいきょう)）\N兄の首は まだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.81,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,Have you yet to take my brother's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Just a little longer, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今しばらく お待ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,朱凶が追っておりますゆえ\Nすぐにも首を持ち帰るはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Zhuxiong is in pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.36,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,so he should be back with his head momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.48,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "should"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:17.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“はず”とは何だ？ “はず”とは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:28.76,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Now, now. Please calm down, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竭氏(けつし)）まあまあ\N落ち着いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竭氏）王弟さま
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:33.58,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(643,510)}Left Chancellor, Jie Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,朱凶以上の刺客は\Nおりません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.88,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,There is no assassin greater than Zhuxiong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.58,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Please be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご安心なされよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.38,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 竭氏　兄のほかにも\Nまだ障害があるのだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.63,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,But Jie Shi, there are still other obstacles besides my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.57,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,Are you taking measures for those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か手を打っているのであろうな？\N（竭氏）抜かりなく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.42,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（迫氏）ほかの しょ… 障害？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Other o-obstacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:52.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ… 分からぬのか？\N（迫氏）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.62,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Are you not aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:59.61,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Changwenjun. I have sent those subordinates that turned Changping to hell in order to dispose of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昌文君(しょうぶんくん)よ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あやつの始末ならば\N長平(ちょうへい)を地獄と化した―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの配下たちを差し向けております\N（成蟜）フフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… “長平の戦い”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.76,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-The battle of Changping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:13.81,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,In that battle, our Qin army drove the Zheng army into a castle, cutting them off from provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（迫氏）あのとき 我が秦国の軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙国(ちょうこく)軍を城に追い詰め\N兵糧を断った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飢えに苦しんだ趙国軍の兵士たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:22.11,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,The Zheng army soldiers suffered from starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:26.22,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,It's said that they started killing each other and eating their flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに殺し合って\Nその肉を食らったという
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:32.67,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,And so, our state of Qin won the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして 戦は我が秦国が勝利した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:36.17,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,But the supreme commander, General Bai Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 総大将であった白起(はくき)将軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.35,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,took the heads of the 50,000 soldiers that were taken prisoner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:42.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捕虜になった５万の兵の首をはね\N40万の兵を生き埋めにした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.38,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,and buried 400,000 soldiers alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.87,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,It was the battle of hell, at Changping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:47.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄の長平の戦い…\Nそ… その配下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.53,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-Those subordinates...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.59,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,Slaughter all those that oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:54.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我に仇(あだ)をなす者は皆殺しにせよ\N（竭氏）御意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.12,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.33,Kingdom-Main,Chenjiao,0,0,0,,That's my chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:59.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ 我が丞相(じょうしょう) フフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）待ちやがれ！\N（徐完）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 俺に勝ったと思ってるのか？\N（徐完）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Do you think you've beaten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:22.61,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,What? Oh, you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（徐完）ほう… まだ息があるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.01,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,But you've utterly lost your composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 気は完全に途切れた\N（信）ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.72,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,I doubt you can stand back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（徐完）もう立てまい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:36.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つ… 強(つえ)え… とてつもなく強え
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.25,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,H-He's strong. Ridiculously strong. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.78,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,He's the one Piao lost to. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂が負けた相手だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.12,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,If I really think about it, I'm no match for someone like him. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えれば\N俺が かなう相手じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.46,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I can't win. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょ… 漂… すまねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.74,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,P-Piao... I'm sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.88,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）信！\N（信）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:14:01.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も考えるな　ただ\N漂の無念を晴らすことだけを考えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.14,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Don't think at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:01.90,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Just keep the idea of avenging Piao in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Avenging Piao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂の無念…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）お前が… お前が…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.83,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.96,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,So you could still stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Never speak Piao's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が漂の名を口にすんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂はな…\N漂は これからだったんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao had everything ahead of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらねえ兄弟ゲンカに\N巻き込みやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And he got caught up in your meaningless brother's quarrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.42,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“くだらん”だと？\N（信）ああ くだらねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.70,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah, meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち底辺の人間には\N誰が王かなんて 興味がないんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:35.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Us humans at the base of society don't give a damn who the king is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなのに… よくも… よくも！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:40.81,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And yet... how could you... how could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ… 死んじまったじゃねえか\Nあいつは もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He's dead, ain't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.63,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He's never...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き返らないんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ… ウウ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速い　しかも 重くなった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.75,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,That was fast! And it was heavier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… 小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.47,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,K-Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）確かに 私と信の実力は\N互角です　しかし―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,It's true that in terms of raw power, Xin and I are equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:20.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,But he is probably stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく信のほうが強いでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:24.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）“信のほうが強い”？\N（漂）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.10,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Xin is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.54,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.58,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,What an odd thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妙なことを言う\Nお前は さっき 互角と申したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say you were equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,When we have matches, we're perfectly equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,試合をすると 全くの互角です\Nしかし―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:39.17,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,But if there's some stalwart opponent that even I can't win against, Xin can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が勝てない猛者がいたとしても\N信なら勝てます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:44.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Are you saying he goes easy on you when you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）お前との対戦は\N手を抜いているということか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）いえ　信は いつも真剣です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.96,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Xin is always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:50.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,For some reason, he's usually equal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうわけか\N私とは互角なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:55.27,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,But if I get even one win against him in a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:55.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）\Nただ 試合でも 私が１つ勝ち越すと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.33,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Xin will definitely win the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の日には 必ず信が勝ちます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,He sounds bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面倒くさそうだな そいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんですよ ハハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.85,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）確かに そうですが でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.59,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,He may be, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）本当に強いですよ 信は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Xin is truly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小僧！ 死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.95,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,You little brat! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ…\N恐ろしいのは これからだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.62,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,The truly terrifying part has only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.48,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,No... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見切り始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.75,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,He's started to give up. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.02,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？ ンンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got, red old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで終わりかよ？ 赤いおっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほざけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.57,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんという小僧だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.77,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,What an incredible kid... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:47.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\N剣をかわしているだけでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.02,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,But if all he does is dodge my sword... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てない　どうする？ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.84,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Then he won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.52,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.76,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,刺客め 焦ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.24,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,You've gotten impatient, assassin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もらった！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.29,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… この俺が…\Nきき… 斬られている…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.72,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,M-Me? C-Cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:24.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.55,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,YOU LITTLE SHIT! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えた！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.56,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,He disappeared!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）大王さま
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:31.49,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,My king, if I were to fall, {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:33.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし私が倒れたときは\N信に おつかまりください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.19,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,please take care of Xin. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,I'm sure that he... {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂）誰よりも高く飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.89,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,will fly higher than anyone else! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんなバカな…\Nこ… この俺が こんな小僧に…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.58,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Th-This can't be! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.42,Kingdom-Thought,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Me...? By this kid...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）これが 信の力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.42,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,This is Xin's power... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,D... Did you feel Piao's vengeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょ… 漂の敵(かたき) 思い知ったか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Did you feel it, you stupid bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い知ったかよ バカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とどめだ！\N（徐完）ま… 待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now I'll finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.20,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってくれ！ お… 俺には家族が…\N４人の子供がいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:14.16,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Please wait! I have a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.98,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,I've got four kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:19.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が死んだら 孤児になる\Nそしたら 一生 奴隷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.95,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,If I die, they'll be orphans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.15,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,And they'll be slaves for their whole lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.43,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Please, just spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか命だけは…\N子供らのために どうか命だけは！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.95,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,For my children's sake, not my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Orphans...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,孤児…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.68,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます\Nありがとうございます…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.19,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.83,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（徐完）あり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.71,Kingdom-Main,Zhuziong,0,0,0,,Than...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の罪と お前の子は関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:45.76,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Your crimes have nothing to do with your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\N次は どうする？ 俺を殺すか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.96,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,What will you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.98,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.82,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしそうなら 俺も\N黙って やられるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.08,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I won't just stay silent and let you do me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を守るために死んでいった人間が\N少なからず いるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:02.58,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,A considerable number of people died in order to keep me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漂も そのうちの１人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.28,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Piao being one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）てめえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You bastard! If you knew that this guy was going to attack him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:15.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつに襲われると知っていながら\Nなぜ漂を見殺しにした？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,why did you let Piao die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）人の命は誰のものでもない\N己だけのものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.85,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,People's lives don't belong to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.31,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Anyone except themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）な… なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.17,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But people have a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）だが 人には“道”がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その命をどう使うか\Nそれが“道”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:28.31,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,The path of how... to use that life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワケ分かんねえこと言って\Nごまかすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.55,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't try to confuse me with crap I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）今のお前には分かるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.19,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,You may not understand now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 漂は大将軍となるために\N俺の身代わりとなった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.69,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,but Piao took my place so that he would become a great general.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが\Nあのとき 漂の選んだ道だったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.61,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,That is the path that Piao chose at that point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は まだ\N自分の道を見つけていないようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.65,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,It seems that you have yet to find your own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,My... path...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.18,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Piao entrusted this state's king to me. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N漂は この国の王を俺に託した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 漂…\Nこいつは お前を殺したも同然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:58.21,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,But this guy practically killed you with his own hands, Piao! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ… どうすりゃいいんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.51,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Dammit...! What am I supposed to do?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてくれ 漂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.13,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Tell me, Piao!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）な… 何のマネだ！\N（政）黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.23,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）マズイな… 分からないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.99,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,This is bad... Do you not see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か今\N地面が かすかに揺れたような…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I just... felt the ground shake a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（迫氏）\N射(う)て！ 動くもの全てが的だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.25,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Anything that moves is a target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,射て！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nな… 何だ？ 何が起こっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.50,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,An army. Quite a large one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍だ　かなり多いぞ\N（信）軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,An army?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人）なに騒いでんだよ？\Nこんな夜更けに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:00.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's all that noise this late at night...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,From over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちからも！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（悲鳴）\N向こうからもか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,W-We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:24.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）か… 囲まれてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなったら 川しか…\N（政）ムリだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.81,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The only way out's through the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:27.88,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,When did they...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲッ！ いつの間に！\N何なんだよ？ これは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）軍系統は\N全て弟側に染まったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.65,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,All of my forces seem to have joined my younger brother. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:43.20,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Even though I sensed the rebellion coming, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦い 反乱を察知しながら\N鎮める力が俺になかった時点で―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.90,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,the moment I no longer had the forces to suppress it, was the battle already over? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は ついていたか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！\Nそれじゃ もうひと暴れするか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:48.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll go another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.20,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,You're intending to fight an army?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 あれと戦う気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ！\Nこんな所で死ねるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.74,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.33,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm dying in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:22:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の首を差し出して\N生き延びるという道もあるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.44,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,If you give them my head, that may grant you a path to survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！ そんなこと\N漂が望んでいるわけねえだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:05.09,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,No way! Piao wouldn't want me to do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.49,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:13.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't have enough strength to run up the hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斜面を駆け上がる力は\N残ってねえから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:14.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,so we'll have to slip through along the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,川沿いを切り抜ける\Nしっかり ついてこいよ！
